{"tid":1404581,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"[遍地開花] 理大員工 支持香港","createTime":"2019-08-04T05:13:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T13:33:55.000Z","uid":292385,"like":49,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e57dc97d652a95c348facb95f1b139d50ae1025b","tid":1404581,"uid":292385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:13:33.000Z","msg":"<strong>[代出POST]</strong><br />\n<br />\n致香港市民：<br />\n<br />\n我是理工大學的一名小職員，<br />\n近一個月來，每天看到同伴受傷或警察的過份武力，<br />\n就有如身同感受，情緒就不禁低落，<br />\n相信有部分人都一樣，<br />\n但在回想自己還有什麼能夠做的時候就發起了這個支持活動。<br />\n<br />\n抱歉，由於小弟文彩一般，<br />\n故此未有寫作一遍公開信，<br />\n只有小弟在收集期間的小小心聲。<br />\n<br />\n上星期小弟在校內發起了收集打氣字句這個活動。<br />\n小弟認為工作在一個教育的地方，<br />\n我們更加有責任站出來，為香港打氣。<br />\n<br />\n雖然貼在校內的單張只有一日就被移走。<br />\n但收集後得來的職員証都超過一百張，<br />\n這個數量可能不及其他的收集活動多，<br />\n但希望亦能為大家打打氣。<br />\n<br />\n收集的期間，接觸到校內不少界別的人士，<br />\n其中亦有包括博士，教授，退休員工及行政員工。<br />\n他們亦有幫忙廣傳此活動，有人更主動捐贈物資。<br />\n在此已經令小弟感到深感安慰及體會到大家團結的力量。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我們每天都身處在一個政府資助的大學內工作，<br />\n但亦有職員都表示曾夢遊參加大部分的活動，<br />\n以及在得到不反對通知書的和平集會中吸過幾次的催淚彈。<br />\n由於參加此活動的有大部分都是合約員工，<br />\n故此很多員工都對反送中事件不敢表態，<br />\n甚至不敢在私人時間談論任何政治。<br />\n<br />\n故此，這些字句是我們作為教育機構內工作而對香港的默默支持。<br />\n在此希望香港人繼續加油！爭取香港人的自由。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AnkscTM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAnkscTM.jpg&h=e4ebf070&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://instagram.com/wearepolystaff?igshid=91ou6q43fiyf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fwearepolystaff%3Figshid%3D91ou6q43fiyf&d=Yc7MVk%2FjSym3Ma7OIK9USHwIqWfEp03u%2FOlStsvMnxY%3D&h=db12c8fb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/wearepolystaff?igshid=91ou6q43fiyf</a>"},{"pid":"433e1b45348193cb37ca3dd3a1a09c28d3c1b24f","tid":1404581,"uid":209566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:37.000Z","msg":"推 埋土好野"},{"pid":"125c05bc54cb9b71c531b5c14f975da813714053","tid":1404581,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9336080b1de53aa6193b47c2390e33d97a5d7a0a","tid":1404581,"uid":292385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:24:38.000Z","msg":"香港加油!"},{"pid":"6e15770d59404967699ead95ad33a1d0e462a56f","tid":1404581,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"67bab6f97f34d495a0a7adc36e412865eb3752e6","tid":1404581,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:26:31.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"ea5cafa7bdaaf6f70d5922dd89450a8bc004ba8b","tid":1404581,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"be9bf60350d5d33c9ef9c77e9cf876d8ef598e50","tid":1404581,"uid":292385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ea5cafa7bdaaf6f70d5922dd89450a8bc004ba8b","tid":1404581,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e15770d59404967699ead95ad33a1d0e462a56f","tid":1404581,"uid":224829,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"125c05bc54cb9b71c531b5c14f975da813714053","tid":1404581,"uid":99499,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:14:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:26:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:27:03.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:30:54.000Z","msg":"要去瘋狂夾三眼仔"},{"pid":"30a4050303c6961a0710980ac2290c210ae2a037","tid":1404581,"uid":224829,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:42:14.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"effd15c5be174a3f5da6cadd7b06adc2132b5191","tid":1404581,"uid":35556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:47:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"444da96612d63eb2017bb8dcf7d448ea0d222b20","tid":1404581,"uid":138707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T05:51:45.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ade98ff6e95b864cb152229d1b3255d587126e79","tid":1404581,"uid":45727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T12:12:23.000Z","msg":"推 理工 ！"},{"pid":"b7efffcc60e68b0fa6e5c7bde7404610dffe08bb","tid":1404581,"uid":292385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T23:57:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1aacca676d0dbd7ffe9d7df9d9457f216865b414","tid":1404581,"uid":299468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T02:40:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"854f7823ecd496319dc49e5a59522a9f194ddd00","tid":1404581,"uid":292385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T11:25:55.000Z","msg":"推推"},{"pid":"2a21b2e84fa54362fcf5260e99a0a4f7efcfca4d","tid":1404581,"uid":292385,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T13:33:55.000Z","msg":"推"}]}